HEADWORD: Invalidate
<hw>In*val"i*date</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Invalidated</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
